---
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-[#EEF7F4]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left Column — Image -->
      <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
        <img
          src="/images/dr-shilpa.png"
          alt="Dr. Shilpa Pandya"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column — Content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <p class="text-[#E8856A] text-sm font-medium italic tracking-wide">
          About the Doctor
        </p>

        <!-- Name -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#2D2A26] leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;">
          Dr. Shilpa Pandya
        </h2>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-[#E8856A] font-semibold">
          Paediatrician &amp; Consultant
        </p>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <p class="text-[#7A7570] leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Shilpa Pandya is a dedicated paediatrician with over 15 years of experience caring for children from infancy through adolescence. She completed her MD in Paediatrics from Gandhi Medical College, Bhopal, and has served families at Hiranandani Hospital, bringing warmth and expertise to every consultation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#7A7570] leading-relaxed">
          She pursued advanced training under MUHS Nashik and completed her internship at the prestigious JJ &amp; Grant Medical Colleges. Her commitment to lifelong learning keeps her at the forefront of evidence-based paediatric practice.
        </p>

        <!-- Credential Badges -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-2">
          <span class="bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-[#2D2A26]">
            MD Paediatrics · Gandhi Medical College, Bhopal
          </span>
          <span class="bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-[#2D2A26]">
            Post Graduate Paediatric Nutrition · Boston University
          </span>
          <span class="bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-[#2D2A26]">
            Lifetime Member · Indian Academy of Paediatrics (IAP)
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Keep away your worries subsection -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#2D2A26]" style="font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;">
          Keep away your worries
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#7A7570] leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Shilpa Pandya specializes in diagnosing and treating a wide range of neonatal and pediatric conditions. Her expertise includes well-baby checkups, immunizations, growth and developmental assessments, behavioral assessments, common pediatric ailments, asthma management, lactation support, and dietary counselling. She is well-versed in emergency newborn and pediatric procedures, including resuscitation, line insertions, and ventilation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#7A7570] leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Shilpa's warm and reassuring demeanor creates a positive and trusting environment, supporting the overall health and well-being of her young patients. Her commitment to excellence, combined with her years of experience, makes her an exceptional pediatrician. She is driven by her passion for providing the highest standard of care and is trusted by parents and caregivers alike.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-lg w-80">
          <img
            src="/images/dr-shilpa-with-baby.avif"
            alt="Dr. Shilpa Pandya with a newborn"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
